snippet.title: Sledding Game Trailer - Store Page Launch - WISHLIST NOW!
snippet.description:
WISHLIST SLEDDING GAME ON STEAM: (https://store.steampowered.com/app/3438850/Sledding_Game/)

Thank you everyone who’s followed along with my journey on Instagram. I can’t thank all of you enough. Having a store page for a game I MADE is something I never thought I’d do.

Even though this feels like a big step, there's still lots more to do. So I hope everyone here can like and share the video, because the next goal is RELEASE!
